text: Stanislav Pokhilko (born 14 June 1975) is a Russian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Russia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
